name: travel-monitoring-analysis-system-tmas-travel-monitoring-analysis-system-461de
notes: Internal FHWA data program that assists in the collection and analysis of data on traffic volumes, vehicle classification, truck weights for traffic statistics, analysis; it is used for development of policies and regulations.  The monthly data are published in the Traffic Volume Trends (TVT) report.
